  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A Nintendo DS game developed by h.a.n.d. Inc. and published by Bandai Namco Games, which was released in Japan in 2011.\n\nThis is an adventure game where you play as Mirumiru, a little girl who found herself teleported to another planet called the Cocoron World.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The goal of the game is to make friends with the residents of the planet Cocoron. It starts in a small area, where you meet 5 creatures.",
